<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 01:28:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Senolytics 与干细胞的结合在小鼠身上显示出希望</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/combining-senolytics-and-stem-cells-shows-promise-in-mice</link><description>与 Immorta Bio 相关的一项新研究表明&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/combining-senolytics-and-stem-cells-shows-promise-in-mice.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 01:27:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/combining-senolytics-and-stem-cells-shows-promise-in-mice</guid></item><item><title>物理学家终于构建了十多年前预测的量子材料</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/physicists-finally-build-a-quantum-material-predicted-more-than-a-decade-ago</link><description>研究人员通过创造一种长期寻求的二维量子材料并确认其不寻常的导电边缘态，实现了一个重要的里程碑。通过应变控制这些状态的能力可能使该材料成为未来室温量子电子学的有前途的平台。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/physicists-finally-build-a-quantum-material-predicted-more-than-a-decade-ago.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 01:12:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/physicists-finally-build-a-quantum-material-predicted-more-than-a-decade-ago</guid></item><item><title>AIE 网络研讨会 — 制作 Horsegirls</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/aie-webinar-making-horsegirls</link><description>与创作团队一起了解广受好评的独立电影《Horsegirls》的幕后故事，将这个非凡的故事变为现实。主持人德文·莫里西 (Devin Morrissey) 与编剧兼导演劳伦·梅耶林 (Lauren Meyering)、女主角莉莲·卡里尔 (Lillian Carrier)、制片人迈克尔·谢尔曼 (Michael Sherman)、麦肯齐·布里登 (Mackenzie Breeden) 和阿利克斯·马迪根-约金 (Alix Madigan-Yorkin)、自闭症敏感性协调员克洛伊·埃斯特尔 (Chloe Estelle) 一起就电影制作过程进行了精彩对话——从发展故事和创作真实的表演到制作、宣传和确保包容性的制作环境。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/aie-webinar-making-horsegirls.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 00:57:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/aie-webinar-making-horsegirls</guid></item><item><title>人工智能教父：一个新物种正在出现——我们无法阻止它 |杰弗里·辛顿（诺贝尔奖）</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-godfather-of-ai-a-new-species-is-emerging-and-we-cant-stop-it-geoffrey-hinton-nobel</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 00:42:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-godfather-of-ai-a-new-species-is-emerging-and-we-cant-stop-it-geoffrey-hinton-nobel</guid></item><item><title>与其他生物不同</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/unlike-other-organisms</link><description>与其他生物体不同，水母水母可以如此迅速地修复损伤，您实际上可以在几分钟内看到小伤口闭合。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/marine-biological-laboratory-mblwoodshole-instagram-photos-and-videos.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 00:27:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/unlike-other-organisms</guid></item><item><title>SensorFM：迈向可穿戴健康数据的通用智能和接口</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/sensorfm-towards-a-general-intelligence-and-interface-for-wearable-health-data</link><description>我们推出了 SensorFM，这是一种可穿戴健康的基础模型，已根据来自 500 万人的超过 1 万亿分钟的传感器数据进行了预训练。通过共同缩放模型大小和数据，SensorFM 学习了人类生理学的通用表示，可转换为 35 个健康预测任务，支持标签高效适应和数据填充，并可以作为个人健康代理的基础工具。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/sensorfm-towards-a-general-intelligence-and-interface-for-wearable-health-data2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 00:12:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/sensorfm-towards-a-general-intelligence-and-interface-for-wearable-health-data</guid></item><item><title>注射可将老年人类卵子中常见的染色体错误风险降低一半</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/injection-halves-risk-of-chromosome-error-common-in-older-human-eggs</link><description>缺少关键蛋白质的卵细胞更有可能最终获得错误数量的染色体，但注射 mRNA 帮助细胞制造蛋白质可以减少这个问题&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/injection-halves-risk-of-chromosome-error-common-in-older-human-eggs2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Jul 2026 23:57:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/injection-halves-risk-of-chromosome-error-common-in-older-human-eggs</guid></item><item><title>Sia表演《Unstoppable》为2025年突破奖颁奖典礼画上圆满句号</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/sia-performs-unstoppable-to-close-the-2025-breakthrough-prize-ceremony</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Jul 2026 23:42:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/sia-performs-unstoppable-to-close-the-2025-breakthrough-prize-ceremony</guid></item><item><title>“量子力学不需要复数”：物理学家首次开发出仅使用“实数”的量子模型</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/complex-numbers-are-not-needed-for-quantum-mechanics-physicists-develop-quantum-model-that-uses-only-real-numbers-for-first-time-ever</link><description>物理学家第一次建立了一个没有复数的量子力学的工作版本——近一个世纪以来，复数一直被认为对该理论至关重要。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/complex-numbers-are-not-needed-for-quantum-mechanics-physicists-develop-quantum-model-that-uses-only-real-numbers-for-first-time-ever.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Jul 2026 23:27:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/complex-numbers-are-not-needed-for-quantum-mechanics-physicists-develop-quantum-model-that-uses-only-real-numbers-for-first-time-ever</guid></item><item><title>人工智能让我们变得愚蠢吗？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/is-ai-making-us-stupid</link><description>不完全是——但我们如何使用它很重要。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/is-ai-making-us-stupid2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Jul 2026 23:12:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/